'''理查德·西摩'''（{{lang-en|Richard Seymour}}，{{bd|1979年|10月6日}}），[[美式足球|美式足球]][[防守截锋|防守截锋]]，曾先后效力于[[国家橄榄球联盟|国家橄榄球联盟]]的[[新英格兰爱国者|新英格兰爱国者]]和[[奥克兰突袭者|奥克兰突袭者]]队。他原先在[[乔治亚大学斗牛犬队|乔治亚大学斗牛犬队]]打球，2001年选秀中被[[新英格兰爱国者|新英格兰爱国者]]队于第一轮第6顺位选中。

他曾七次入选[[明星碗|明星碗]]，五次入选全明星队（All-Pro），并随爱国者队三夺[[超级碗|超级碗]]冠军。有些人认为西摩是NFL中最好的防守内锋。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/sports/football/nfl/patriots/2006-05-31-seymour-sw_x.htm|title=If you have just one lineman, make it Seymour|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|first=Chris|last=Colston|date=2006-05-31|accessdate=2009-05-18|archive-date=2010-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100117143133/http://www.usatoday.com/sports/football/nfl/patriots/2006-05-31-seymour-sw_x.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.yahoo.com/nfl/news?slug=jc-offday101106&prov=yhoo&type=lgns|title=Breakfast of champions|work=[[Yahoo!_Sports|Yahoo! Sports]]|first=Jason|last=Cole|date=2006-10-11|accessdate=2009-05-18|archive-date=2006-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061114042854/http://sports.yahoo.com/nfl/news?slug=jc-offday101106&prov=yhoo&type=lgns|dead-url=no}}</ref>他也被认为是历史上最出色的选秀第6顺位球员。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.yahoo.com/nfl/news;_ylt=Atp0tT5Eudz9oRbEVKq7Wk05nYcB?slug=cr-bestfirstroundpicks042307&prov=yhoo&type=lgns|title=Best all-time first-round picks|work=[[Yahoo!_Sports|Yahoo! Sports]]|first=Charles|last=Robinson|date=2007-04-23|accessdate=2009-05-18}}</ref>

西摩入选明星碗的场上位置包括4-3阵型防守截锋与3-4阵型防守端锋。此外他偶尔也会在短码数（short yardage）与位于得分线（goal line）的情况下充当[[全卫|全卫]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.ign.com/articles/565/565952p2.html|title=Richard Seymour Interview|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|first=Jon|last=Robinson|date=2004-11-12|accessdate=2009-05-18|archive-date=2012-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120215204627/http://sports.ign.com/articles/565/565952p2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>不过自2005年对[[圣迭戈闪电|圣迭戈闪电]]比赛的一码达阵中膝盖受伤后，他就未再担任过全卫。<ref name="Fullback">{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/nfl/news/story?id=2185140|title=Patriots will be without DE Seymour against Atlanta|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|date=2005-10-08|accessdate=2009-05-19|archive-date=2012-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102220401/http://sports.espn.go.com/nfl/news/story?id=2185140|dead-url=no}}</ref>

